{"tid":2405454,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"鐵鏈下的心形手 - 陳也","createTime":"2021-02-12T11:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T11:08:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e726192322118f32540eb724b0353622ddb7bd3a","tid":2405454,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210212/R346MBOJTBFHZB3MRNZSXKC2YA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210212%2FR346MBOJTBFHZB3MRNZSXKC2YA%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=34ea07f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210212%2FR346MBOJTBFHZB3MRNZSXKC2YA%2F&h=f61ed657\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210212/R346MBOJTBFHZB3MRNZSXKC2YA/</a><br />\n<br />\n鐵鏈下的心形手 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/M1Wvur0ue5bTC2kc1pCcQiWEMSo=/1440x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GRTCAAI4JBFPZN67PLE6GJQS5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FM1Wvur0ue5bTC2kc1pCcQiWEMSo%3D%2F1440x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGRTCAAI4JBFPZN67PLE6GJQS5Y.jpg&h=02446cb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在市集看到畫師illustracy的喵塔羅，將塔羅牌變晒貓樣，很Q。我唔係貓奴，唔識玩塔羅，唔知點解連黃大仙神籤也未求過的當時，就是想買一盒。檔主說可以幫我即場測一下，問我想問乜。除了香港，還是香港。她說自己近日測過，三張牌命中晒。「過去」那一張，是錢幣6。貓大爺拎住秤撒幣，兩頭貓屈膝跪地求財得財。「現在」是寶劍6，黃貓泛舟遠去。「未來」一張是權杖2，智者貓手執地球模型望向遠方的山與海。回家看圖解牌，喵畫簡單，門外漢都識解。於是我滿懷肥佬黎的神心，洗牌，由老公誠摯抽牌，抽出三張：過去：大牌中的國王，明解。現在：權杖9，這是緊守崗位永不放棄的卡，貓頭紮住繃帶但緊緊扶住權杖。未來的一張，是大牌中的教皇，信賴、感悟、精神導師集一身。最後抽出一張整體大局，是錢幣1。代表新開始與穩定。卡中一隻大貓手，原本捧住的金色五角星變成了黃色貓爪印。<br />\n<br />\n好牌無改變到終院五位法官對肥佬黎的判決。我抹去眼淚，記住肥佬黎鐵鏈下的心形手，與塔羅貓連登豬繼續努力。"}]}